OL,3,CHospital issues warning after
OL,4,Cnorovirus outbreak on wards
OL,6,F, issuing a statement on 26 April
OL,7,F2024, said: "A norovirus outbreak is
OL,8,Faffecting six wards at Royal Bolton
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,F"We're asking visitors to thoroughly
OL,12,Fwash their hands to help stop its
OL,13,Fspread and protect patients, staff and
OL,14,Fothers from the virus. Handwashing
OL,15,Ffacilities are available throughout
OL,16,Fthe hospital.
