OL,3,CHospital issues warning after
OL,4,Cnorovirus outbreak on wards
OL,6,F"This can be done by thoroughly
OL,7,Fwashing your hands with soap and
OL,8,Fwater, and if you'd like to take extra
OL,9,Fsteps you can ask on our wards for
OL,10,FPPE," she added.
OL,12,F"To check whether your loved one's
OL,13,Fward is affected before you visit you
OL,14,Fcan call the ward directly, where a
OL,15,Fmember of staff will best advise you,"
OL,16,FLianne continued.
OL,18,F"Thank you for all your help as we
OL,19,Fmanage this outbreak."
